{"tid":780753,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"亞馬遜 真「嚇伏」，請大家幫手決定佢既評分！(重貼)","createTime":"2018-08-15T11:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T08:24:08.000Z","uid":201136,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"45140c33ec48b4370604b9e35da73fc842279944","tid":780753,"uid":201136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T11:28:48.000Z","msg":"(新人重post，改晒d 5字，多多見諒 )<br />\n相信大家都有聽過 Amazon Web Services，但原來大公司d 客服可以好伏。<br />\n<br />\n話說我個帳號A login 唔到，重設密碼條link 改唔到新密碼，所以我用另一個帳號 B登入，回報帳號A問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/185312_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F185312_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png&h=6ef31ae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(set 乜新密碼都話有error)<br />\n<br />\n琴晚收到個AWS美國staff，佢就send 番條重設密碼 link 比我，叫我改password 就可以，跟著我就比負評佢個reply<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/185533_418715ca8a3e333c43494f3b3bbec44a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F185533_418715ca8a3e333c43494f3b3bbec44a.png&h=ac3f7930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n負評一出，過左無幾耐就收到個美國電話，個staff 就打來了解事情，我同佢講，我個問題係重設唔到新密碼，你又send 番條link 比我做乜。最後佢都無能為力，話唔可以幫我set密碼，要搵其他人幫我手。<br />\n<br />\n以為件事過一段落，點知之後佢email 話會比 Mandarin-speaking representatives 去跟進。我心諗，大陸果d 會唔會仲伏，點知真係好既唔靈醜既靈，頭先下晝收到個中文email 同我講，個case close 左啦，你可以登入舊acc (帳號A) 再回報關於帳號A既問題！我DKLM，登入唔到仲叫我登入去回報問題！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/184802_a840a9dd9efb9ea51a9c50177f08a191.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F184802_a840a9dd9efb9ea51a9c50177f08a191.jpeg&h=e5837cf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我跟手又送佢一個負評<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/185533_418715ca8a3e333c43494f3b3bbec44a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F185533_418715ca8a3e333c43494f3b3bbec44a.png&h=ac3f7930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不出所料，過左無耐又有一個電話打來講國語，佢話唔好意思，之前諗唔到你login 唔到，是佢諗得不夠清楚。不過同佢傾完都係幫我唔到改密碼，都係日後跟進咁，點知原來好戲在後頭！佢話我頭先在評分果度比好低，可唔可以改高d！我心諗，DKLM，原來搞咁耐就係為左佢個評分，而且面皮好厚下！不過我都好心軟地同佢講好啦，但我d 朋友都話佢地抵死，所以我想請大家幫下手。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得我應唔應該幫佢改高分d？"},{"pid":"25dfef9697f53898468cb89f28ede1e6673b3d26","tid":780753,"uid":130044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T11:36:46.000Z","msg":"改<br />\n利申 打手"},{"pid":"260411bec4677590744241f044d79c5579ffa2c1","tid":780753,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T11:38:57.000Z","msg":"咁既service <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc2117d88a0984452389d46ab9ac8589e2f1f13","tid":780753,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T11:40:55.000Z","msg":"點都唔改 睇下佢點"},{"pid":"8226793c20ef5ae6c793286189bde7cd9bd8e16c","tid":780753,"uid":66822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T11:47:05.000Z","msg":"個負評好有威力"},{"pid":"774bad84bec4eb0f0fe088880a32a2d3889fef04","tid":780753,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T11:49:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ede0b8d327d29d8324a1defc14b0db444cae2c8","tid":780753,"uid":145320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T11:52:47.000Z","msg":"負評佢地會影響雙糧 bonus 仲會比supervisor 捉去屌加收warning<br />\n利申發夢見到"},{"pid":"4a8834cb6fbf092a077ef317f083d16e19cad9b0","tid":780753,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:40:19.000Z","msg":"唔出奇<br />\n我返工個主任唔記得左 login 密碼，搵 it reset 密碼，過幾日打電話黎話 reset 左，新密碼 send 左去佢個 email 到"},{"pid":"d05ff8829f8743c6a6f183a9f0d616f934753c1a","tid":780753,"uid":79375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T06:12:24.000Z","msg":"九唔答八的回覆點俾高分佢地"},{"pid":"16ea36508fff9ffad0d8e7ced2d106cae6a8be8e","tid":780753,"uid":79869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T06:50:54.000Z","msg":"你同佢講，如果你幫我follow up<br />\n而我又拎得返個account, 就畀返d分"},{"pid":"62eaee5e7d60bac21f298360d7fa604e862a78fe","tid":780753,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:24:08.000Z","msg":"PayPal 一鳩樣，唔記得密碼要 Reset Password，收到 E-Mail 個 Verify Code，要再收埋 SMS，但個電碼號碼原來入錯左。<br />\n電郵佢地都係叫我 Login Update 個電話收 Code <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}